# gemini-improve-ui map

**Stack**: WXT 3 (Chrome MV3), TypeScript, content script on `https://gemini.google.com/*`. Details: root `README.md`.

| Path | Role |
| --- | --- |
| `entrypoints/content/index.ts` | Content script entry — wires all `src/*` init, custom CSS injection |
| `entrypoints/options/` | Options page (`index.html`, `main.ts`) |
| `wxt.config.ts` | Extension manifest, permissions, WXT runner (Chrome path, debug port) |
| `src/settings.ts` | Defaults + `chrome.storage.sync` keys |
| `src/keyboard.ts` | Shortcuts, action button position |
| `src/chat.ts` | Chat page behavior |
| `src/autocomplete.ts` | Autocomplete + search-field autocomplete |
| `src/deep-dive.ts` | Deep Dive mode |
| `src/export.ts` | Chat → YAML/Markdown export, save flow |
| `src/map.ts` | Turn map / scroll UI |
| `src/search.ts` | Search page integration |
| `src/history.ts` | History selection mode |
| `src/dom-analyzer.ts` | DOM export / analysis (e.g. Ctrl+Shift+D) |
| `src/quick-prompts.ts` | Quick prompt buttons |
| `src/types.d.ts` | Ambient / shared types |
| `dev.sh` | Debug Chrome + MCP workflow |
| `eslint.config.js` | ESLint flat config |

**External refs**: [WXT](https://wxt.dev/), [Chrome extensions](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions).
